  <div class="row">
  	<div class="col-md-9">	
   			<div class="article-content ArticleContent" itemprop="articleBody"><p>If you’d like your events&nbsp;to show in the main blog loop along with your other posts, go to Events &gt; Settings and check the option that says “Include events in main blog loop” on the General Settings tab.</p>

<p>Once that is checked, your events will show alongside your blog posts. By default, they will show in order by the event date. You can also customize it with <a href="641498-Order-events-in-main-blog-loop-by-post-date">this tutorial</a> so that your events show in the blog by date of publication.</p>
</div>    			
